dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights (with depths shown by soundings in inset maps).
Color legend shows Turkish, Bulgarian, and Greek territories; also railroads, forts, fortresses.
Also sea routes, waterways, marsh/swampland, roads, cities.
